    "description": "RESTful API for a Project & Task Management System.\n\nBase URL: {{baseUrl}}\nAuth: Bearer {{token}}\n\n## Auth Flow\n1. Call `Auth / Register` to create a user.\n2. Call `Auth / Login` to obtain a JWT `access_token`.\n3. The token is stored in the `token` environment variable automatically and used by all protected requests.",
